column1: Daily Weather Observations for Murrurundi, New South Wales for July 2021
Prepared at 13:01 UTC on Sunday 17 October 2021   IDCJDW2196.202107
Observations for Murrurundi are now taken at a site in Haydon Street, replacing those from the Post Office.
